        <p align=3D"left"><font face=3D"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>SE=
CTION
        3. WHAT IS AN EXPONENT?</b></font></p>
        <hr noshade=3D"">	=09
        <table width=3D"175" border=3D"1" align=3D"right" cellpadding=3D"0"=
 cellspacing=3D"0">
          <tbody><tr>
            <td><ul>
                <li><font size=3D"2" face=3D"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">=
